title: Wholesale Establishment means an establishment, wholly or partly engaged in wholesale trade, manufacturers‘ wholesale outlets including related storage facilities, A
clause_text: Wholesale Establishment means an establishment, wholly or partly engaged in wholesale trade, manufacturers‘ wholesale outlets including related storage facilities, A.P.M.C. establishments, warehouses and establishments engaged in truck transport including truck transport booking agencies;
